                Invic&amp;lt;t&amp;gt;o <lb n="2"/><expan><abbr>Aur</abbr><ex>elius</ex></expan> Mon<lb break="no" n="3"/>tanus <expan><abbr>mil</abbr><ex>es</ex></expan> <lb n="4"/><expan><abbr>leg</abbr><ex>ionis</ex></expan> V <expan><abbr>M</abbr><ex>acedonicae</ex></expan> &amp;lt;p=I&amp;gt;(iae)<certainty match="preceding-sibling::node()" locus="value"/> <expan><abbr>c</abbr><ex>onstantis</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>f</abbr><ex>elicis</ex></expan><certainty match="preceding-sibling::node()" locus="value"/> <lb n="5"/><expan><abbr>l</abbr><ex>ibens</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>p</abbr><ex>osuit</ex></expan> 
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Z. 1: Buchstabe V in Form von Y. Z. 4: Bujor: i(nvictae); statt f(elicis) auch p(iae) möglich. (B): CIL III: Z. 4: leg. V Mace.; AE 1967: Z. 4/5: p(iae) l(ibens).</p>
            </div>
